{"tid":1895533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利右翼：斷航、管制邊境、強制隔離...過去我們不是一直發出警告？但有聽嗎？沒有，它把我們的警告扣上排外的大帽子！","createTime":"2020-02-24T14:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T16:09:52.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc270375912ac40539147ecb20baee1f8eceb90f","tid":1895533,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"---------------------------------------<br />\n//右派的薩爾瓦尼：「斷航、管制邊境、強制隔離所有疫區人士...過去幾周我們不是一直發出警告？但中央政府有聽嗎？沒有，他們就繼續把我們的警告扣上『種族主義』、『排外』、『惟恐天下不亂』的大帽子，然後現在疫情大爆炸了，就說吧！」砲火四射的薩爾維尼表示：<br />\n<br />\n「孔蒂和他的菁英部長們千萬不要向我道歉，我才不稀罕你們的抹黑。你們真正該做的，是向6,000萬義大利人道歉，因為你們讓國民失望、沒有捍衛守護國民的健康。快道歉！然後馬上辭職下台！」//<br />\n<br />\n義大利疫情失控：威尼斯嘉年華被迫中斷，極右激辯「國境封鎖」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4366141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4366141&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=7c86c3a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4366141</a>"},{"pid":"ecea243d93a2aa00752da941da44508651303637","tid":1895533,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"我地香港人早就叫全世界封關啦<br />\n聽條世衛共狗講真係死得"},{"pid":"3c80ac17c32362021256d580e98bafe12232cc3c","tid":1895533,"uid":346806,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"岩，根本唔係極右，係本土派"},{"pid":"ffd0efa2299f5bd706120c6b2fa954bd6d6718fe","tid":1895533,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"又係死左膠禍國殃民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf8e9e2db4167b286bc744fe65eb1db627d77b7","tid":1895533,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"Push"}